{"tid":1323618,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方：以公平公正及不偏不倚態度處理所有公眾集會遊行","createTime":"2019-07-16T09:57:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T11:33:53.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"92fd8856790973e2821c3f104b4bb3800026bc37","tid":1323618,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:57:07.000Z","msg":"民建聯立法會議員蔣麗芸去信警務處處長盧偉聰，要求警方在處理遊行集會申請時，若判斷可能會引起騷亂，涉及影響公共安寧及秩序，應暫停發出「不反對通知書」。<br />\n<br />\n警方回覆本台查詢時說，尊重市民表達意見、言論及集會的自由，並根據香港法律，以公平、公正和不偏不倚的態度處理所有公眾集會、遊行及示威活動。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，根據《公安條例》，如果警務處認為有需要維護國家安全、公共安全、公共秩序或保護他人的權利，可禁止舉行任何已作出通知的公眾集會，或反對公眾遊行的舉行。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1468666-20190716.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1468666-20190716.htm&d=FVRAyOQFEUVrsg2I2pbTeY%2FVxAEwmAwDimrVtn2syv4%3D&h=2d22cab1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1468666-20190716.htm&h=473c4179\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1468666-20190716.htm</a>"},{"pid":"b8d26738aac182ff313358fd72fd9d46afe3e7ae","tid":1323618,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:58:10.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n以為tvb講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96848b0f41bc68290ed250557091f1207bf18471","tid":1323618,"uid":99608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:59:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>蔣議員，建議你少講啲冇用既說話</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"8a2c4551d46bc43086a7c4cad0c68ab63dd56d2e","tid":1323618,"uid":225977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:59:28.000Z","msg":"一視同仁咁行行下衝入去打鳩人丫嘛<br />\n我好擔心17號啲老人家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}